<a class="xref" href="http://chemapps.stolaf.edu/jmol/docs/index.htm?ver=14.2#polyhedra">polyhedra</a> have been created. See also 
<b>polyhera(n)</b>, below. (Jmol 14.4)</td ></tr >
<tr >
<td valign="top" >chemical elements</td >
