<td>
<blockquote>
<p >
<i >Centers the model on a specified 
<a class="xref" href="http://chemapps.stolaf.edu/jmol/docs/index.htm?ver=14.2#draw">draw</a> object</i ></p ></blockquote></td></tr> 
