<blockquote>
<p >
<i >Resets the radius of the halo to the default 
<a class="xref" href="http://chemapps.stolaf.edu/jmol/docs/index.htm?ver=14.2#spacefill">spacefill</a> radius.</i ></p ></blockquote></td></tr> 
