<td valign="top">
<a id="k856"> </a>set xxx</td ></tr>
<tr name='tr_set'>
<td>
<blockquote>
<p >
<i >
<b>set</b> followed by a Jmol parameter xxx is the same as 
<b>set xxx TRUE</b>.</i ></p ></blockquote></td></tr> 
